data.title: The Runaways
data.meta_description: The Runaways were an American all-girl rock band. They were formed in Los Angeles in 1975 and split in 1979. They were not a major success in the United States. They were popular in some other countries Like Japan.
data.text:
The Runaways were an American all-girl rock band. They were formed in Los Angeles in 1975 and split in 1979. They were not a major success in the United States. They were popular in some other countries Like Japan.

Their signature song was "Cherry Bomb".
